816
01:12:24,915 --> 01:12:26,349
[growls]

817
01:12:28,485 --> 01:12:29,753
Let him be!

818
01:12:32,355 --> 01:12:34,691
[growling]

819
01:12:44,902 --> 01:12:45,903
[clatter]

820
01:12:55,445 --> 01:12:56,646
You think that'll hold him?

