Can you go lower?

847
01:14:57,700 --> 01:14:59,837
Wait. Wait, wait!

848
01:14:59,870 --> 01:15:01,437
Go back up slowly.

849
01:15:05,809 --> 01:15:06,676
Stop!

850
01:15:11,916 --> 01:15:12,782
