851
01:15:15,085 --> 01:15:15,953
[gasps]

852
01:15:28,065 --> 01:15:29,632
[coughing]

853
01:15:35,738 --> 01:15:36,606
We got it.

854
01:15:37,875 --> 01:15:38,943
We got it!

